entry.title: New release for Rundeck: v4.17.5-20240304
entry.content:
Release v4.17.5

What's Changed

  • RSE-886: Fix: Job option description too long by @github-actions in https://github.com/rundeck/rundeck/pull/8794
  • RSE-903: Rdcli is not working properly updating projects on severals rundeck versions by @ltamaster in https://github.com/rundeck/rundeck/pull/8880
  • RUN-2213: Update Postgres driver to patch CVE-2024-1597 by @github-actions in https://github.com/rundeck/rundeck/pull/8943
  • RUN-2216: [backport] Update spring to 5.3.32 because CVE-2024-22243 by @ahormazabal in https://github.com/rundeck/rundeck/pull/8963
  • Update remote docker to use default version for release/4.17.x branch. by @chrismcg14 in https://github.com/rundeck/rundeck/pull/8979

Full Changelog: https://github.com/rundeck/rundeck/compare/v4.17.4...v4.17.5
